thread.title: Keller, Schmid, Myernick enter National Soccer Hall of Fame

title: Keller, Schmid, Myernick enter National Soccer Hall of Fame
text:
> Sports Keller, Schmid, Myernick enter National Soccer Hall of Fame Travis Myernick, son of Glenn "Mooch" Myernick, sheds a tear as he accepts his fathers induction into the National Soccer Hall of Fame at the Museum of History and Industry, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Seattle, Wash. (Sy Bean/The Seattle Times via AP)
